## ğŸ§  Overview

- This project focuses on data gathering, assessment, cleaning, and analysis using the WeRateDogs Twitter dataset.
- The goal is to wrangle data from multiple sources, assess its quality and tidiness, clean it programmatically, and perform meaningful analysis and visualizations to derive insights.
- This project demonstrates the data wrangling process as part of a data analysis workflow, integrating manual inspection, Python-based cleaning, and automated data merging.

