ğŸ“Š Example Insights

The most common dog ratings are above 10/10 (WeRateDogsâ€™ humorous rating style).

Tweets with images of dogs generally have higher engagement (favorites and retweets).

Certain breeds (as predicted by the image classifier) receive more attention on social media.

